<li><i>Storyteller: The Official Guide to the Works of Orson Scott Card</i>, Michael R. Collings, Overlook Connection Press, 2001, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/189295026X" class="internal">ISBN 1-892950-26-X</a></li>
</ul>
